{"id":683047,"date":"2023-12-30T10:20:36","date_gmt":"2023-12-30T04:50:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/?p=683047"},"modified":"2024-01-05T10:23:20","modified_gmt":"2024-01-05T04:53:20","slug":"why-pursue-online-degree-from-sikkim-manipal-university","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/why-pursue-online-degree-from-sikkim-manipal-university","title":{"rendered":"10 reasons to pursue an online degree from SMU"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Ever since its inception in the year 1995, Sikkim Manipal University (SMU) has helped thousands of students pave a path for a glorious career through its quality education. Now, this top university located in north-east India has opened its doors to enthusiastic students who can\u2019t commute to the campus owing to their personal or professional commitments. Thanks to the Online Manipal platform, students from anywhere can pursue online degree courses from Sikkim Manipal University at their convenience.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>UGC-entitled degrees, expert faculty, robust Manipal alumni status, affordable fees, and comprehensive curriculum are some of the key <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/what-makes-online-manipal-degrees-a-great-choice\">advantages of online degrees from SMU<\/a><strong>. <\/strong>What makes Sikkim Manipal University better than other universities is its commitment to offering student-centric learning using innovative instructional approaches for the overall holistic development of the students.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you still wondering why to chose Sikkim Manipal and not any other university to pursue an online course? You will get not one but 10 reasons to choose SMU for online degree programs in this post, so don\u2019t go anywhere and read this complete post.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-top-reasons-to-choose-smu-for-your-online-degree\"><strong>Top reasons to choose SMU for your online degree<\/strong>\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are ample reasons to choose Sikkim Manipal University for an online UG or PG course. But we understand your concern about why you should choose only SMU and not any other university for the same course.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, we thought of sharing 10 benefits of pursuing online education at SMU:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>UGC-entitled degrees:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>The prime reason to choose Sikkim Manipal University (SMU) for an online degree course is its globally acknowledged accreditation and recognition. Sikkim Manipal University is a National Assessment and Accreditation Council (NAAC) A+ accredited institution that offers UGC-entitled degrees to its students.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"2\">\n<li>Scholarship opportunities:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Another thing that makes Sikkim Manipal University stand apart from leading universities is its <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/top-scholarships-offered-by-sikkim-manipal-university-for-online-programs\">exciting scholarship opportunities<\/a> to encourage students to pursue higher education.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This leading university located in north-east India boasts 5 types of scholarships that are listed below in the table:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Type of Scholarship<\/strong><\/th><th><strong><br>Eligibility<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>Scholarship Percentage<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Candidates from Sikkim and Northeast India<\/strong><\/td><td>Reserved for candidates from Sikkim and northeast IndiaApplicant must provide a valid proof of address<\/td><td>30% scholarship<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Defense Personnel<\/strong><\/td><td>Reserved for eligible defense personnelApplicant must provide the ID or service number of the defense sector<\/td><td>20% scholarship<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Divyaang<\/strong><\/td><td>Reserved for candidates with disabilitiesApplicant must present a valid certificate from an authorized healthcare professional about the disability status<\/td><td>20% scholarship<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Alumni of Sikkim Manipal University<\/strong><\/td><td>Reserved for UG and PG graduate alumni of Sikkim Manipal UniversityApplicant must provide the degree earned by the university<\/td><td>20% scholarship<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Meritorious Students<\/strong><\/td><td>Reserved for students who have scored 80% or above in 10+2 or a UG courseApplicant must provide the mark sheet provided with a recognized board<\/td><td>10% scholarship<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"3\">\n<li>Affordability:<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Sikkim Manipal University (SMU) scores high by offering low-cost online degree programs. Students need not hesitate to pursue higher education anymore, by enrolling in affordable online degree courses from Sikkim Manipal University. Moreover, the university makes it easier for students to focus on their studies rather than on financing their studies by offering them a flexible payment mode with no-cost EMI payments.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"4\">\n<li>Expert faculty:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Get the golden opportunity to study from the expert faculty of Sikkim Manipal University from anywhere through an online degree program. The experienced professors and teachers at the university will not only provide valuable insights but will clear all your doubts, thereby offering you specialization in your chosen online UG or PG course from Sikkim Manipal University.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"5\">\n<li>Placement assistance:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Sikkim Manipal University not only impacts quality education through its online degree courses but also helps students with exceptional placement assistance. It helps students reach out to industries that can give them wings to establish a bright career with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/placements\">placement assistance services<\/a> like industry-readiness sessions, mock interviews, skill assessments, resume building, and virtual placement drives.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"6\">\n<li>Prestigious Manipal alumni status:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Who doesn\u2019t want to get the label of the glorious Manipal group in the resume? This is what makes SMU a top choice for online education. Sikkim Manipal University is counted among India&#8217;s top 100-150 universities according to NIRF and proudly enjoys the 1st rank in the list of top private universities in North East in 2023 according to IIRF. This is not all; SMU has grabbed the 6th rank in the top multidisciplinary universities in the east zone as per THE WEEK. So, pursuing an online degree from this university means enjoying the prestigious Manipal alumni status.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"7\">\n<li>Diverse classroom:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>When listing the unique features of online degrees at SMU, it is impossible to miss mentioning its diverse classroom. The most significant advantage of studying online through a top-notch university like Sikkim Manipal University is getting the opportunity to be part of a diverse peer group of people from all backgrounds, geographical locations, and cultures. The global classrooms of Sikkim Manipal University, through the Online Manipal platform, help online students connect with learners from over 1500 cities and 50 countries.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"8\">\n<li>Exhaustive e-content:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/who-should-pursue-online-ba\"><strong>Pursuing an online BA<\/strong><\/a> or any other degree from Sikkim Manipal University is more than just live classes. Students get access to exhaustive e-content in the form of e-books and other e-learning material on diverse subjects. They are encouraged to interact with subject matter experts to expand their knowledge base and grab skills peculiar to their chosen course. This is not all; they also get to access the monthly newspapers to update themselves with the latest academic information from the university. The same newsletter acknowledges the student and faculty achievers from time to time to boost their confidence.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"9\">\n<li>Industry simulations &amp; webinars:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Another feather in the cap of Sikkim Manipal University that appeals to students who want to pursue an online degree course is its 360-degree learning experience. The university emphasizes interactive learning methodology and holds expert sessions and webinars to engage the students in their chosen fields of specialization. They start with a virtual orientation of each fresh batch and then gradually introduce them to an all-in-one enhanced digital learning platform with the latest industry stimulations and doubt-clearing sessions. All this is done through the<a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/transforming-virtual-learning-the-online-manipal-way\"> Sikkim Manipal University\u2019s Learning Management System (LMS)<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\" start=\"10\">\n<li>Online proctored exams:&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Students who study online for any undergraduate or postgraduate degree course at Sikkim Manipal University can conveniently appear in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/what-is-the-examination-process-for-online-degree-students\">online proctored exams<\/a><strong>, <\/strong>which are no less than real-life exams and are monitored virtually. They can take the exam from anywhere, and an online proctor will keep a watch on the candidate&#8217;s activity during the exam via a webcam. This allows these online students to take the exam on a convenient day and pick a suitable time.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-conclusion\"><strong>Conclusion\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know the endless reasons to pursue online degree courses from Sikkim Manipal University, it is time we update you with the types of online degree courses offered at SMU through the Online Manipal platform, so have a look:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/bachelor-of-arts\">Bachelor of Arts (BA)&nbsp;<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-bcom-smu?utm_source=Google&amp;utm_medium=CPC&amp;utm_campaign=SRCH_SMU_Brand_BCom&amp;utm_content=BCom_SMU_Exact&amp;utm_keyword=sikkim%20manipal%20university%20bcom&amp;matchtype=e&amp;utm_adset=g&amp;utm_placement=&amp;utm_position=20746860138&amp;gclid=CjwKCAiA98WrBhAYEiwA2WvhOoa6xPJVfR0wBjObHVDmOANFyaHGgAt129VW31-TVQKz_Oeg_fvcnRoCX1cQAvD_BwE\">Bachelor of Commerce (BCom)<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/master-of-commerce-smu#:~:text=Online%20MCom%20is%20a%20two,the%20degree%20is%204%20years.\">Master of Commerce (MCom)<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/master-of-arts-english\">Master of Arts (MA) in English<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/smu.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/us-ca\/master-of-arts-sociology#:~:text=What%20are%20some%20key%20subjects,ethnicity%20%26%20nationalism%2C%20and%20more.\">Master of Arts (MA) in Sociology<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/SMU-MA-Political-Science-Domestic-Brochure.pdf\">Master of Arts (MA) in Political Science<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mca-smu?utm_source=Google&amp;utm_medium=CPC&amp;utm_campaign=SRCH_SMU_Brand_MCA&amp;utm_content=MCA_SMU_Phrase&amp;utm_keyword=sikkim%20manipal%20university%20online%20mca&amp;matchtype=p&amp;utm_adset=g&amp;utm_placement=&amp;utm_position=20746859928&amp;gclid=CjwKCAiA98WrBhAYEiwA2WvhOveQAIPjT7O7J64I9re6_II5yi10PxtYtG0mjTklRD39AV131im4jRoC0kAQAvD_BwE\">Master of Computer Applications (MCA)<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are keen to enjoy flexibility and quality education at affordable pricing, then Sikkim Manipal University is the right choice for you to pursue an online degree program. The university equips students with the skills and knowledge needed to thrive in today&#8217;s competitive and AI-integrated world. Rest assured, the degrees you will get after an online course hold the same value as that of a traditional campus degree, so gear up and embark upon a journey to accommodate higher education with online degree courses at SMU without sacrificing your job or other personal commitments.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ever since its inception in the year 1995, Sikkim Manipal University (SMU) has helped thousands of students pave a path for a glorious career through its quality education. Now, this top university located in north-east India has opened its doors to enthusiastic students who can\u2019t commute to the campus owing to their personal or professional [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":19,"featured_media":682355,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[218,26],"tags":[19,220],"class_list":["post-683047","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-arts","category-general","tag-online-degree","tag-sikkim-manipal-university"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>10 reasons to pursue an online degree from SMU - Online Manipal<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Why pursue an online course from Sikkim Manipal University, Best online degree course at SMU, 10 reasons to study online from SMU.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"noindex, nofollow\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"10 reasons to pursue an online degree from SMU - Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Why pursue an online course from Sikkim Manipal University, Best online degree course at SMU, 10 reasons to study online from SMU.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/why-pursue-online-degree-from-sikkim-manipal-university\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:publisher\" content=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2023-12-30T04:50:36+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2024-01-05T04:53:20+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/Top-government-jobs-online-BA-students-can-apply-for@2x-100.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1412\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"791\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/>\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"Editorial Team\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:label1\" content=\"Written by\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data1\" content=\"Editorial Team\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:label2\" content=\"Estimated reading time\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data2\" content=\"6 minutes\" \/>\n<script type=\"application\/ld+json\" class=\"yoast-schema-graph\">{\"@context\":\"https:\\\/\\\/schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\